  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个send_notification的状态流转图，核心是WorkerNode检测到有文件要上传时的处理流程。起始状态应该是WAITING_FILE，从WorkerNode触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "WAITING_FILE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以WorkerNode到WAITING_FILE的触发条件是'有文件需要上传'。那WAITING_FILE之后直接到SENDING状态吗？还是需要经过LoadBalancer？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WAITING_FILE",
        "SENDING",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "WAITING_FILE之后直接流转到SENDING。但SENDING状态有两个入口——除了从WAITING_FILE过来，当没有文件的时候，LoadBalancer也会直接进入SENDING。两个触发条件要分开标注。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WAITING_FILE",
        "SENDING",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画好了这两个入口。SENDING之后呢？看起来应该有个注册实体的步骤。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SENDING",
        "REGISTERED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，SENDING之后是REGISTERED，表示在SEND系统里创建了实体。这里要分叉——如果实际上传了文件，就到UPLOADED；如果没有文件要上传，直接跳到COMPLETE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "REGISTERED",
        "UPLOADED",
        "COMPLETE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：REGISTERED到COMPLETE的标注是'No file da caricare'，REGISTERED到UPLOADED是'File caricati'，然后UPLOADED再到COMPLETE。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "REGISTERED",
        "UPLOADED",
        "COMPLETE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错。最后COMPLETE要流转到ACCEPTED，这个状态是SEND系统也认可的终态。然后ACCEPTED需要落到RedisCache做缓存。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMPLETE",
        "ACCEPTED",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "整个流程都画完了：从WorkerNode检测文件开始，经过SENDING、REGISTERED，根据是否有文件分别走UPLOADED或直接到COMPLETE，最后统一ACCEPTED并写入RedisCache。标题用'Stati send_notification'可以吗？",
